skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lad quiz
des:
Some of the questions we will ask include:
"Do you like sport?"
"Do you go to the gym?"
"Have you ever changed the wheel on a car?"

By answering yes or no to these questions we will be able to give you a 100% accurate lad score, are you lad enough to play?

Can girls play this game? Of course you can, you can show your man who wears the trousers in your house!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
